data.description: LOW HOA FEES of $125/MONTH! Take the long drive up to this lovingly maintained home where you are first greeted with mature and majestic oak trees. You have arrived at your new home at 15830 Gleneagle Ct in the McGregor Woods community! Lush landscaping surrounds this home on a little over 1/3 acre. Front private patio for your morning beverage, or nap, in a quiet and peaceful area. Walk right in and you will be delighted with the view straight out to the beautiful salt water pool and spa with enormous deck area. It is all ready for you to enjoy with family & friends. This panoramic-screened lanai area + pool/spa area is super private, no neighbors to see on any side of you! Multiple sliders take you outside. You will be pleasantly surprised with tall ceilings, 3 large BR and 2 baths and a 2 car garage. Plantation shutters on all windows. Enjoy cooking in your new kitchen, living area with wood burning fireplace, and eat-in-kitchen. Dining and living rooms too. Laundry/pantry conveniently located right off the kitchen. A 50 year warranted metal standing seam roof will protect you for years to come. Come see what this home has to offer....you will be pleasantly surprised!
